    "/agents/{agent_id}/history": {
      "get": {
        "description": "Return the last *limit* completed task records for *agent_id*.\n\nEach record contains:\n- ``task_id``: unique task identifier\n- ``prompt``: the task prompt text\n- ``started_at``: ISO timestamp when the task was dispatched\n- ``finished_at``: ISO timestamp when the RESULT arrived\n- ``duration_s``: wall-clock seconds from dispatch to RESULT\n- ``status``: ``\"success\"`` or ``\"error\"``\n- ``error``: error message string, or null on success\n\nResults are ordered most-recent-first.  Pass ``?limit=N`` to control\nhow many records are returned (default 50, capped at 200).\n\nDesign reference: TAMAS (IBM, 2025) \"Beyond Black-Box Benchmarking:\nObservability, Analytics, and Optimization of Agentic Systems\"\narXiv:2503.06745 \u2014 per-agent task history enables bottleneck analysis.\nLangfuse \"AI Agent Observability\" (2024): tracing decision paths.",
        "operationId": "agent_history_agents__agent_id__history_get",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "in": "path",
            "name": "agent_id",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "title": "Agent Id",
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          {
            "in": "query",
            "name": "limit",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "default": 50,
              "title": "Limit",
              "type": "integer"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "items": {},
                  "title": "Response Agent History Agents  Agent Id  History Get",
                  "type": "array"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Successful Response"
          },
          "422": {
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Validation Error"
          }
        },
        "summary": "Per-agent task history"
      }
    },
